mixin about()
    section#about.about-section
        .container
            .about-section__card
                header.about-section__card-header
                    h2 Web Applications for portfolio management
                    h4 Do it faster, do it better!
                .about-section__card-info
                    p Our asset management software will support you in your daily basis tasks such as asset and portfolio management, automatic flows with custodian banks and brokers, back and middle office activities, risk management, and report generation.
                    blockquote
                        p We developed a web application that your team can run in any device (from pc to tablet and smartphone).
                    p Your team will use the same application (with the possibility to set different permissions for each person of team) using a unique database, saving time and money.
